    "causal_summary": "The goal plugin works but is operationally opaque and one-way in places: archived goals in `<stateDir>/.archive/` (`mk-goal.js:635,828`) are invisible to operators; there is no health/doctor introspection despite the dir-walk machinery already existing (`mk-goal.js:874-902`); `pause` is one-way from the command surface (`goalopencode.md` routes no resume, `GOALACTIONS` at `mk-goal.js:71` has none); the tool accepts `tokenBudget` (`mk-goal.js:1862`) but `goalopencode.md` never routes it; autonomy caps `DEFAULTMAXAUTOTURNS`/`DEFAULTMAXWALLMS` are hardcoded (`mk-goal.js:30,32`) while char caps",
